Nancy's Reconnaissance trip for Onda Gallery's Visual Arts Tour, Buenos Aires, Argentina

This is the little slideshow that I presented at Onda Gallery for Alan Oliver's proposed Visual Art Tour to Buenos Aires. Although the trip has been postponed, we are hoping to offer it in a few years. In the meantime you can enjoy your own visual art tour of the Paris of South American with a side trip to Iguazu Falls. Please note that a trip such as this can also be customized for individuals with the exception that most of the private collections may be available to groups only! Saludos! Nancy
